# Compliance artifacts — generated on demand by the Compliance workflow
# (scripts/generate-sbom.mjs / generate-notices.mjs) into dist/compliance/.
# Not versioned: they are derived from the dependency tree and shipped as CI
# artifacts, not source. Already covered by the `dist` rule above; listed
# explicitly so the artifact location stays documented.
dist/compliance/
